#: gui/dialogs.py:482
msgid ""
"Some websites show a browser verification page (for example a Cloudflare challenge) before their feeds. To read them in BlindRSS:\n"
"1. Open the website in your web browser and wait for it to load.\n"
"2. Export its cookies with a \"cookies.txt\" browser extension.\n"
"3. Choose the exported file below.\n"
"Also paste your browser's User-Agent string (search the web for \"what is my user agent\" to see it) so the site accepts the cookies."
msgstr ""
"Sommige websites tonen vóór hun feeds een browserverificatiepagina (bijvoorbeeld een Cloudflare-controle). Zo leest u ze in BlindRSS:\n"
"1. Open de website in uw webbrowser en wacht tot deze is geladen.\n"
"2. Exporteer de cookies met een \"cookies.txt\"-browserextensie.\n"
"3. Kies hieronder het geëxporteerde bestand.\n"
"Plak ook de User-Agent-tekenreeks van uw browser (zoek op internet naar \"what is my user agent\") zodat de site de cookies accepteert."

#: gui/dialogs.py:500
msgid "Import from &Browser..."
msgstr "Importeren uit &browser..."

#: gui/dialogs.py:506
msgid "Get the \"Get cookies.txt LOCALLY\" extension for Chrome-based browsers"
msgstr ""
"De extensie \"Get cookies.txt LOCALLY\" voor op Chrome gebaseerde browsers "
"ophalen"

#: gui/dialogs.py:523
msgid "&Browse..."
msgstr "Bladeren..."

#: gui/dialogs.py:574
msgid ""
"No supported browser profiles were found.\n"
"\n"
"Cookies can be read directly from Firefox-based browsers (Firefox, LibreWolf, Waterfox, Floorp, Zen). Chrome-based browsers encrypt their cookies; use the \"Get cookies.txt LOCALLY\" extension linked above and import the exported file instead."
msgstr ""
"Geen ondersteunde browserprofielen gevonden.\n"
"\n"
"Cookies kunnen rechtstreeks worden gelezen uit op Firefox gebaseerde browsers (Firefox, LibreWolf, Waterfox, Floorp, Zen). Op Chrome gebaseerde browsers versleutelen hun cookies; gebruik de hierboven gelinkte extensie \"Get cookies.txt LOCALLY\" en importeer het geëxporteerde bestand."

